long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Transform your browsing experience with Sidebar For ChatGPT - Free Access, the ultimate Chrome extension that seamlessly integrates ChatGPT into any website. No API required—just click, and you're ready to chat!

Key Features:
Instant Access: Open the ChatGPT sidebar effortlessly by clicking the extension icon, using the shortcut Ctrl + Space, or right-clicking to select "Open Sidebar for ChatGPT."

Versatile Usage: Whether you're researching, writing, or simply curious, ChatGPT is at your fingertips, ready to assist you across all tabs and websites.

User-Friendly Interface: Enjoy a sleek, unobtrusive design that keeps your focus on your tasks while providing easy access to ChatGPT whenever you need it.

Completely Free: Experience all the benefits of ChatGPT without any cost—forever! No subscriptions, no hidden fees.

Elevate your productivity and make the most of your online experience with Sidebar For ChatGPT - Free Access. Install now and bring the power of AI into your daily browsing!

Disclaimer:
This extension is not affiliated with or officially endorsed by OpenAI.
